    "Maria is an anthropomorphic Nidoqueen, a wild one at that."

    "How she got hyperpregnant :"

    "Maria once a normal Nidoqueen, running around and acting like a pokemon."

    "One day, she found in the wilds a tiger-skinned bikini swimsuit on the ground."

    "Although most Pokemon would leave it because they don't see an interest in it, made her interested in it."

    "As she tried to put it on out of pretending to be fashioned, she had felt an immense change from her body."

    "She had taken off out of fear that it would change her body forever. But it was already too late."

    "Now she got a feminine hyperpregnant body carrying 24 babies in her womb"

    "She was completely terrified by it, that she had tried in so many pokemon centers to figure out how to reverse it."

    "Only to realize that she had to stay like that until she either give birth or die."

    "Now she's working alongside Dijonay, as she has grown used to be hyperpregnant, wearing this tiger-skinned bikini."

